game.name: Superhero Pregnant Emergency
game.description:
Our mommy to be has an important day to day job, she is a superhero! In her last mission she got a little injured so she needs the best doctor in town to treat her. Play with the tools you find in the emergency room and learn how to use them. Listen to the superhero heartbeat, find the fractured bones and make sure they heal well. The mommy will be ready for new adventures in no time!

Pregnancy is a wonderful time to experience in the life of almost every woman. Superhero is also no different from the common ladies like you! We have today got you covered with a brand new girls game where you will meet with a gorgeous superwoman who needs medical attention anytime. She has got some unwanted injuries during her last mission and reached to your hospital to get the best treatment. Join Superhero Pregnant Emergency and be prepared to take care of her in the optimum way possible!

You are the best doctor of the city so do not need to be scared of when you treat her. The emergency room is full of the needful medical equipment and tools required to give her the needful treatment. All you need to do is just learn how to use them to complete multiple tasks in this HTML5 doctor game. Start with listening to her heartbeat with the stethoscope and then fixing the fractured bones with the help of other medical equipment!

Make sure to follow all the procedures you need to make her heal fast. Put your strong doctoring abilities to the test to go on the new adventures with your favorite superhero in this brand new girls game! We feature a great number of top-liked hospital surgery games for girls and boys that are playable on multiple devices like desktops, mobile phones, tablets and iPads or iPhones. Good luck to save as many patients as you can in our other free hospital simulators, no download required!
